column2: Absolutely beautiful day.  Very light breeze and lots of people swimming in the water.
0.25" of rain the day before- small bass jumping in schools- calm- and light breeze - perfect day.
School of small bass jumping- clear skies- calm- sunny- and absolutely quiet- no one on lake.
Partly sunny- calm and quiet- lots of water bugs on surface- lots of monarch butterflies- and tiny minnows in shallows.
Calm- clear- ducks on lake.  Almost 2" rain in previous 4 days.
Clear and calm- slight breeze- muggy- no rain.
Moderate wind- clear sky.  No rain.
Beautiful day- no breeze.  Had 3 days straight of rain previously (9/12-9/14).
Very windy but sunny.  No measurable rain lately.
